content.p: A warm welcome to all students who are studying abroad with us here at the University of Nottingham Malaysia. We hope you enjoy your time at the Malaysia Campus and make new friends from around the world and gain a different cultural perspective in your studies. Malaysia is an exciting, diverse country that offers visitors a range of unique cultural experiences. The proximity of the campus to Kuala Lumpur gives students a great opportunity to explore one of the most exciting and dynamic capital cities in Southeast Asia. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8778 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8005
